author: stephan
msg: Minor bug fixes in preperation for 1.0  prettyPrint is no longer a static
variable.  I can actually see why you would want some elements to be or not
to be prettyPrinted i.e.:PRE also you may want TR to be pretty printed but TD
not to be, this allows for that.  Changed Attributes and ElementAttributes to
return Element for addAttribute and removeAttribute this allows you to chain
methods on an element as long as you don't call addElement you would have to
call addElementToRegistry (as defined in the interface.)
